          <name xml:lang="en">carbon content, fossil</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">dimensionless</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">C content calculated out of (input) shredder fraction composition in Tab 4.47 (ecoinvent v2.2 report 18_V). Carbon content in plastic was calculated using data in Tab A.2, ecoinvent v2.2 report 13_I. Others was also considered plastic, and calculated the same way (from pg 70, ecoinvent v2.2 report 18_V). Ferro was assumed to have a C content of 0.012 kg C/ kg  (C content of steel, calculated out of emission factors published in Commission Decision of 18 July 2007 establishing guidelines for the monitoring and reporting of greenhouse gas emissions pursuant to Directive 2003/87/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council (notified under document number C(2007) 3416)). The other component of the fraction were considered to content no C.</comment>
        </property>
